@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #2F4F4F
skinparam DefaultTextAlignment center

left to right direction

title C2 - Arquitectura mTLS inter-servicio S2 (baseline, istio-mtls, linkerd-mtls)

actor "k6 S2 runner" as k6

node "Namespace mubench-real" {
  component "auth-service" as auth
  component "api-service" as api
  component "data-service" as data
  database "postgres" as db
}

cloud "Plano de confianza" {
  component "Istio sidecar\n(Envoy)" as envoy
  component "Linkerd proxy" as linkerd
}

k6 --> auth : HTTP NodePort 30184 (/login)
k6 --> api : HTTP NodePort 30181 (/profile,/users)
api --> data : llamada interna
data --> db : consulta SQL

api ..> envoy : C2/istio-mtls
auth ..> envoy : C2/istio-mtls
data ..> envoy : C2/istio-mtls

api ..> linkerd : C2/linkerd-mtls
auth ..> linkerd : C2/linkerd-mtls
data ..> linkerd : C2/linkerd-mtls

note right of envoy
C2/istio-mtls:
- inyeccion de sidecar Istio
- Certificados mTLS entre pods
end note

note right of linkerd
C2/linkerd-mtls:
- inyeccion linkerd.io/inject=enabled
- mTLS automatico entre proxies
end note

note bottom
C2/baseline: trafico inter-servicio en texto plano (sin sidecar mTLS).
En S2 final, el benchmark de C2 entra por NodePort HTTP.
end note

@enduml
